body:
The modpack aims to create an interesting adventure atmosphere with buildings, dungeons and biomes, complementing this with other mods that you will obviously want to see in your survival.

You will definitely want to download this modpack, because here you can: create mechanisms, weapons, food, fly to other planets, build your factories, fight monsters in dungeons, explore the world with one of the best world generators. 

Main mods:
1. Let's Do: Vinery (and other Let's Do mods);
2. Portfolio;
3. Infinity Buttons;
4. YUNG's Mods;
5. Ad Astra;
6. Create (with addons);
7. Farmer's Delight (with addons);
8. Fabric Seasons (with addons);
9. Better Combat;
10. Rechiseled;
11. Beautify;
12. Spyglass Astronomy;
13. Naturalist;
14. Reinforced Mods;
15. RPG Series Mods;
16. Inmis;
17. Nullscape;
18. Incendium;
19. Regions Unexplored;
20. Mythic Metals;
21. Simply Swords;
22. Immersive Armors;
23. Supplementaries;
24. CTOV (with addons);
25. Automobility;
26. Another Furniture;
27. Immersive Aircraft;
28. Handcrafted.
